icious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-360x361.jpg 360w, https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-200x200.jpg 200w, https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-320x320.jpg 320w, https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-480x480.jpg 480w, https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-720x720.jpg 720w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" data-pin-description="This smooth, velvety Curried Cauliflower Soup recipe is easy, healthy, vegan, low carb, low fat, and a low calorie density food, and also deliciously filling and hearty! #lowcalorie #noomdiet #vegansoup #lowcarbsoup" data-pin-media="https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2.jpg" data-lazy-src="https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-500x500.jpg"><noscript><img decoding="async" width="500" height="500" src="https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-500x500.jpg" class=" fsri-image wp-post-image" alt="A bowl of curried cauliflower soup on a blue towel with a spoon, garnished with cauliflower florets and grated zucchini." data-pin-nopin="true" aria-hidden="true" srcset="https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-360x361.jpg 360w, https://www.bowlofdelicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Curried-Cauliflower-Soup-2-200x200.jpg 20