<div class="wprm-recipe-template-redesign-2021-container">
	<div class="wprm-recipe-template-redesign-2021-header">
		<h2 class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">Sheet Pan Tandoori Salmon with Burst Cherry Tomatoes</h2>
		<div class="wprm-spacer" style="height: 5px;"></div>
		<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">A broiler is a great substitute for a tandoor in this tandoori salmon recipe due to its high heat. Salmon, coated in a tandoori spiced yogurt mixture, and cherry tomatoes with garlic are cooked for only about 10 minutes under the broiler, resulting in a gorgeous char on both the fish and vegetables.</span></div>
